.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-FEE-POLICY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-fee-policy \- show local fee policy for all active channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-fee-policy
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the locally-announced fee policy for each
.B CHANNELD_NORMAL
channel: base fee, proportional fee (ppm), and HTLC size limits.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, base_fee_msat, fee_ppm,
  htlc_min_msat, htlc_max_msat}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-set-fee (1),
.BR lightning-node-fee-revenue (1)
